      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"goblin\" thing... i don't think i can do that. i don't have that kind of energy left. it's not just about being bored or lonely, it's like the actual substance of my life is gone. he was the part of me that actually interacted with the world. without him, i feel like i'm already dead, just walking around in a body that doesn't belong to me anymore. everything feels completely pointless.",
